description: The SPDR EURO STOXX 50 ETF seeks to provide investment results that, before fees and expenses, correspond generally to the total return performance of the EURO STOXX 50 Index (the “Index”)The EURO STOXX 50 Index is designed to represent the performance of some of the largest companies across components of the 20 EURO STOXX Supersector IndexesThe Index captures approximately 60% of the free-float market capitalization of the EURO STOXX Total Market Index
name: SPDR EURO STOXX 50 ETF
